product_name: Victorinox Limited Edition Dual-Compartment Monosling Daypack
long_description: The Victorinox Limited Edition Dual-Compartment Monosling Daypack is ideal for everyday use and features a small, easy-access pocket on the shoulder strap that's large enough to fit your iPhone(R). Large main compartment has zipper closure; zippered front compartment with snap cover contains an interior slash pocket. Padded back panel and adjustable shoulder strap maximize comfort. Victorinox Limited Edition Dual-Compartment Monosling Daypack is made from durable fabric with an abrasion-resistant ballistic nylon base. Limited edition green camo print incorporates the Victorinox logo; bright orange accents and lining add pop.
